<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif">Me: record is an instruction to a compiler to make a type from a signature, write the comparison and copying as well. </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif">TLDR </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif">define a&#160;</font><a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/csharp/language-reference/builtin-types/reference-types" data-linktype="relative-path" style="color: black; text-decoration: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal"><font color="black" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="16px">reference type</font></a><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif">&#160; </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif">that provides built-in functionality for encapsulating data </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="16px">The term</font><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif">&#160;</font><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="16px"><em style="color: rgb(22, 22, 22); font-family: Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">record</em></font><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif">&#160;</font><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="16px">is used to describe behavior that applies to all record types. Either</font><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif">&#160;</font><code style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-left: 0; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal"><font face="SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, Courier, monospace" size="13.6px" color="rgb(22, 22, 22)">record struct</font></code><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif">&#160;</font><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="16px">or</font><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif">&#160;</font><code style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-left: 0; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal"><font face="SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, Courier, monospace" size="13.6px" color="rgb(22, 22, 22)">record class</font></code><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif">&#160;</font><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="16px">is used to describe behavior that applies to only struct or class types, respectively.</font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>

</richcontent>
