<richcontent TYPE="NOTE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <span style="color: rgb(22, 22, 22); font-family: Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none"><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="16px">Init-only properties, whether created from positional parameters (</font></span><code style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-left: 0; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal"><font face="SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, Courier, monospace" size="13.6px" color="rgb(22, 22, 22)">record class</font></code><span style="color: rgb(22, 22, 22); font-family: Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none"><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="16px">, and</font></span><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="16px"><span>&#160;</span></font><code style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-left: 0; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal"><font face="SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, Courier, monospace" size="13.6px" color="rgb(22, 22, 22)">readonly record struct</font></code><span style="color: rgb(22, 22, 22); font-family: Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none"><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="16px">) or by specifying</font></span><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="16px"><span>&#160;</span></font><code style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-left: 0; color: rgb(22, 22, 22); font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal"><font face="SFMono-Regular, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Menlo, Courier, monospace" size="13.6px" color="rgb(22, 22, 22)">init</font></code><span><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="16px">&#160;</font></span><font color="rgb(22, 22, 22)" face="Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size="16px"><span style="color: rgb(22, 22, 22); font-family: Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none">accessors, have</span><span>&#160;</span><em style="color: rgb(22, 22, 22); font-family: Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">shallow immutability</em><span style="color: rgb(22, 22, 22); font-family: Segoe UI, SegoeUI, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none">. After initialization, you can't change the value of value-type properties or the reference of reference-type properties.</span></font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>

</richcontent>
